ome, consider which walls would be best used to showcase a single showpiece image or a creative wall gallery from this session. Perfect display areas can be anything from a blank wall to one which already contains portrait art from a previous session.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">During our appointment you will be able view your images, see our albums and framing options and create wall gallery collections for a truly custom experience.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">While planning your order, don&rsquo;t forget to consider the people in your life who would love to receive the thoughtful gift of beautiful portraiture for an upcoming holiday, birthday, celebration, or&ndash; better yet &ndash; for no reason other than the fact you were thinking of them!</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">I really look forward to sharing your finished images with you. Having peeked at a couple already, I know you are going to be over the moon