ries, or makeup materials. We strongly suggest bringing props as they really do add that extra personalised touch to your experience!</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">As far as clothing, keep it simple. Throw in a little colour if you&rsquo;d like, but avoid the busy patterns and please don&rsquo;t feel the need to match everyone in white shirts.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">Keep the clothing casual, colourful, and try to avoid logo or branded clothing as this will date. Our sessions are relaxed and comfortable, so make sure you feel comfortable with what clothing you bring. We have plenty of time to change, and use a selection of your clothing items.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">At the end of our shoot, we will make a time for you to come back and view your beautiful images in our cinematic viewing room.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; 