tline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">My style of photography is both casual and natural, as I feel the best images are taken when your family is less aware of the camera. In this way I capture more natural moments between you instead of directing you to look, speak, or pose yourselves in specific ways :-)</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">Because kids are kids, I may ask for parents to step outside and out of view. This is to ensure the best, most natural images possible since children have a tendency to react differently when parents are in the room.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">I encourage snacks for children, but to avoid any spills, stains, and dirty cheeks! Hahaha!</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">At the end of our session, we will lock in a time for the presentation appointment. I will also send you home with a planning guide. Please use this guide to note where you plan to place your wall portraits, which family and friends will be receiving images as gifts, and which albums or custom books may be of interest, along with any of our other unique and beautiful products.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">The presentation appointment takes place during regular business hours at the studio, and lasts approximately 90 minutes. Thanks to cutting edge studio software, we are able to mock up wall groupings and album recommendations with all your favorite images.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">Additionally, I will provide artistic input on wall galleries, placement in your home, and size given your budget, style, and personal taste.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">Since your order will be taken at the presentation appointment, make sure all who wish to have input regarding your order are present at this time.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">Woohoo, that's it for now! I'll be in touch with you again to confirm everything just before our shoot.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">I can't wait to work with you guys! And as always, if you have any questions, suggestions or just want to chat, please get in touch with me anytime.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;" /></p> <p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2px; line-height: 22px; outline: none; word-break: keep-all; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; word-break: keep-all;">Cheers,</span></p>
